<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>{{ post.title }} | {{ site_title }}</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ post.summary }}">
<meta name="keywords" content="{{ keywords }}">
<meta name="author" content="{{ site_title }}">
<meta name="robots" content="index, follow">

<!-- Open Graph -->
<meta property="og:type" content="article">
<meta property="og:title" content="{{ post.title }}">
<meta property="og:description" content="{{ post.summary }}">
<meta property="og:url" content="{{ site_url }}/posts/{{ post.post_no }}.html">
<meta property="og:site_name" content="{{ site_title }}">
<meta property="article:published_time" content="{{ post.published }}">

<!-- Canonical: 미러 페이지 자체를 정본으로 (구글이 이걸 색인) -->
<link rel="canonical" href="{{ site_url }}/posts/{{ post.post_no }}.html">

<!-- JSON-LD 구조화 데이터 -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": {{ post.title|tojson }},
  "description": {{ post.summary|tojson }},
  "datePublished": "{{ post.published }}",
  "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": {{ site_title|tojson }} },
  "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": {{ site_title|tojson }} },
  "mainEntityOfPage": "{{ site_url }}/posts/{{ post.post_no }}.html"
}
</script>

<style>
  :root {
    --fg: #222;
    --muted: #666;
    --accent: #0b5ed7;
    --bg: #fff;
    --border: #e5e7eb;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Malgun Gothic", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", sans-serif;
    margin: 0; padding: 0; color: var(--fg); background: var(--bg);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  header, footer {
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: none; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
  header a.home { color: var(--fg); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
  main {
    max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }
  h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; line-height: 1.3; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
  .meta { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .content { word-break: keep-all; }
  .content img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; }
  .cta {
    margin-top: 3rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;
  }
  .cta a {
    display: inline-block; padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem; background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .cta a:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
  .cta p { margin: 0 0 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <a class="home" href="{{ site_url }}/">{{ site_title }}</a>
</header>

<main>
  <article>
    <h1>{{ post.title }}</h1>
    <div class="meta">발행일: {{ post.published[:10] }}</div>
    <div class="content">
      {{ post.body_html|safe }}
    </div>

    <div class="cta">
      <p>네이버 블로그에서 원문 전체와 댓글을 확인하실 수 있습니다.</p>
      <a href="{{ post.original_url }}" rel="noopener">네이버 블로그에서 원문 보기 →</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</main>

<footer>
  <div style="max-width:760px; margin:0 auto;">
    © {{ site_title }} · <a href="{{ site_url }}/">전체 글 보기</a>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
